INSERT INTO `packages` VALUES (1,'Set sail on the \'Rivers of Brunei\' and immerse yourself in a journey that weaves through pristine rainforests, vibrant water villages, and untamed wildlife.','Brunei','Set sail on the \'Rivers of Brunei\' and immerse yourself in a journey that weaves through pristine rainforests, vibrant water villages, and untamed wildlife. Glide along the serene waters of the Brunei River, witness elusive proboscis monkeys, and discover the enchanting Kampong Ayer—Asia’s largest stilt village. This tour is more than a trip; it’s an exploration of Brunei’s hidden gems and cultural treasures, all from the river’s unique vantage point. Don’t miss your chance to uncover the secrets of Brunei from its waters — secure your spot today and let the adventure begin!','2025-03-17','img/packages/001_Brunei_Resized_jpg/001_img_1020_6.jpg','The Rivers of Bandar Seri Begawan',4,3,800.00,'2025-03-14',1,'img/packages/001_Brunei_Resized_jpg/001_img_1020_4.jpg','img/packages/001_Brunei_Resized_jpg/001_img_1020_8.jpg','img/packages/001_Brunei_Resized_jpg/001_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/001_Brunei_Resized_jpg/001_img_1020_3.jpg'),(2,'Dive into Brunei’s rich culinary heritage with our \'Food Galore Brunei\' tour, where every bite tells a story.','Brunei','Calling all food lovers! Dive into Brunei’s rich culinary heritage with our \'Food Galore Brunei\' tour, where every bite tells a story. Savor mouth-watering delights from bustling \'Pasar Malam\' markets and hidden local street food gems— from fragrant satay and spicy nasi katok to the sweet allure of kuih-muih. Meet local chefs, discover secret spots, and taste the flavors that make Brunei a food lover\'s paradise. Whether you’re a foodie or an adventurer, this delicious journey will leave you craving more. Don’t miss out—reserve your spot now and let your taste buds explore Brunei!','2025-05-12','img/packages/002_Brunei_Resized_jpg/002_img_1020_3.jpg','Food Galore Brunei',3,2,500.00,'2025-05-10',2,'img/packages/002_Brunei_Resized_jpg/002_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/002_Brunei_Resized_jpg/002_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/002_Brunei_Resized_jpg/002_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/002_Brunei_Resized_jpg/002_img_1020_4.jpg'),(3,'Feel the warm embrace of the sun and the soft caress of the sand with our \'Danang Sands\' tour package!','Vietnam','Feel the warm embrace of the sun and the soft caress of the sand with our \'Danang Sands\' tour package! Discover Da Nang’s stunning coastline, where pristine beaches meet azure waters, and hidden coves beckon you to explore. Unwind in luxury beach resorts, marvel at the beauty of the Marble Mountains, and savor fresh seafood at vibrant seaside markets. Whether you seek adventure or pure relaxation, this is your ultimate beach getaway. Don’t wait—book your \'Danang Sands\' experience now and let the waves wash your worries away!','2024-11-18','img/packages/003_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/003_img_1020_1.jpg','Danang Sands',5,4,1000.00,'2024-11-14',1,'img/packages/003_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/003_img_1020_7.jpg','img/packages/003_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/003_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/003_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/003_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/003_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/003_img_1020_4.jpg'),(4,'Embark on a breathtaking adventure with our \'Sapa Rice Trails\' tour!','Vietnam','Embark on a breathtaking adventure with our \'Sapa Rice Trails\' tour! Discover a world beyond the bustle of Hanoi to the emerald-green rice terraces of Sapa, where mist-covered mountains meet cascading fields and traditional hill tribes welcome you with their vibrant culture. Hike along scenic trails, enjoy panoramic views, and experience the rhythm of rural life. With every step, you’ll uncover a new layer of Vietnam’s beauty, from hidden waterfalls to charming local markets. Don’t just see Sapa—feel it! Sign up for \'Sapa Rice Trails\' today and immerse yourself in a journey that will linger in your heart forever!','2024-12-08','img/packages/004_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/004_img_1020_2.jpg','Sapa Rice Trails',6,5,2400.00,'2024-12-03',1,'img/packages/004_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/004_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/004_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/004_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/004_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/004_img_1020_3.jpg','img/packages/004_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/004_img_1020_4.jpg'),(5,'Step into a world of mystique with our \'Pagodas of Perfume\' tour!','Vietnam','Step into a world of mystique with our \'Pagodas of Perfume\' tour! Journey through lush valleys and along the serene Yen Stream to the breathtaking Perfume Pagoda, a sacred site hidden amidst stunning limestone cliffs. Discover ancient temples, marvel at intricate carvings, and immerse yourself in the spiritual aura and culture of Vietnam’s most revered pilgrimage destination. With every turn, feel the history and culture that have enchanted visitors for centuries. Don’t miss this chance to explore a hidden gem of Vietnam—book your \'Pagodas of Perfume\' experience now and let the serenity of this sacred place captivate you!','2024-11-10','img/packages/005_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/005_img_1020_1.jpg','Pagodas of Perfume',6,5,1500.00,'2024-11-05',5,'img/packages/005_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/005_img_1020_8.jpg','img/packages/005_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/005_img_1020_10.jpg','img/packages/005_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/005_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/005_Vietnam_Resized_jpg/005_img_1020_5.jpg'),(6,'Join us on the \'Alor Alor Kuala Lumpur\' tour, where the vibrant streets of Jalan Alor come alive with tantalizing aromas and flavors!','Malaysia','Join us on the \'Alor Alor Kuala Lumpur\' tour, where the vibrant streets of Jalan Alor come alive with tantalizing aromas and flavors! Wander through Kuala Lumpur’s most famous food street, sampling sizzling satay, savory laksa, and sweet cendol from bustling hawker stalls, from Jalan Alor to Pasar Seni! Mingle with locals, discover hidden gems, and experience the heartbeat of Malaysia’s culinary scene. This is more than a food tour; it’s a feast for the senses in the heart of Kuala Lumpur! Don’t miss your chance to taste the best of KL—reserve your spot on \'Alor Alor Kuala Lumpur\' today and indulge in an unforgettable food adventure!','2024-12-09','img/packages/006_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/006_img_1020_6.jpg','Alor Alor\' Kuala Lumpur',3,2,350.00,'2024-12-07',2,'img/packages/006_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/006_img_1020_3.jpg','img/packages/006_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/006_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/006_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/006_img_1020_7.jpg','img/packages/006_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/006_img_1020_8.jpg'),(7,'Bask under the endless blue skies of Borneo with our \'Kuching Blue Skies\' tour package!','Malaysia','Bask under the endless blue skies of Borneo with our \'Kuching Blue Skies\' tour package! Explore the charming city of Kuching, where history meets nature along the meandering Sarawak River. Wander through vibrant markets, marvel at colonial architecture, and take in stunning views of Mount Santubong. Venture into lush rainforests, meet orangutans in their natural habitat, and uncover the magic of hidden waterfalls. Whether you seek cultural immersion or thrilling adventure, this tour offers it all. Don’t let this chance to experience Borneo’s hidden gem slip by—book your \'Kuching Blue Skies\' escape today!','2024-10-19','img/packages/007_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/007_img_1020_4.jpg','Kuching Blue Skies',5,4,900.00,'2024-10-15',1,'img/packages/007_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/007_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/007_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/007_img_1020_7.jpg','img/packages/007_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/007_img_1020_8.jpg','img/packages/007_Malaysia_Resized_jpg/007_img_1020_6.jpg'),(8,'Escape to the breathtaking highlands with our \'Azure Shan State\' tour!','Myanmar','Escape to the breathtaking highlands with our \'Azure Shan State\' tour! Discover Myanmar\'s hidden gem, where rolling hills meet vibrant blue skies and emerald tea plantations stretch as far as the eye can see. Explore the enchanting Inle Lake, with its floating gardens and stilted villages, or wander through bustling local markets and ancient pagodas. Enjoy the hospitality of the Shan people and savor authentic cuisine in picturesque temperate settings. Whether you’re an adventurer or a cultural explorer, Shan State promises unforgettable moments. Don’t wait—reserve your \'Azure Shan State\' journey now and immerse yourself in its unspoiled beauty!','2025-01-17','img/packages/008_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/008_img_1020_3.jpg','Azure Shan State',7,6,3500.00,'2025-01-10',1,'img/packages/008_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/008_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/008_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/008_img_1020_7.jpg','img/packages/008_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/008_img_1020_8.jpg','img/packages/008_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/008_img_1020_1.jpg'),(9,'Dive into the vibrant celebration of Myanmar\'s New Year with our \'Thingyan Water Lights\' tour!','Myanmar','Dive into the vibrant celebration of Myanmar\'s New Year with our \'Thingyan Water Lights\' tour! Experience the exhilarating Thingyan Water Festival, where streets come alive with water fights, colorful parades, and dazzling lights. Dance to the beat of traditional music, join in the joyous water-splashing, and witness the stunning illuminated floats gliding through the night. It\'s a time of renewal, joy, and unforgettable fun! Don’t miss your chance to be part of this cultural extravaganza—sign up for the \'Thingyan Water Lights\' tour now and celebrate like never before!','2025-03-23','img/packages/009_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/009_img_1020_7.jpg','Thingyan Water Lights',4,3,1400.00,'2025-03-20',3,'img/packages/009_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/009_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/009_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/009_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/009_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/009_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/009_Myanmar_Resized_jpg/009_img_1020_6.jpg'),(10,'Elevate your cosmopolitan adventure with our \'Singapore Skyline & Thrills\' tour!','Singapore','Elevate your cosmopolitan adventure with our \'Singapore Skyline & Thrills\' tour! Marvel at the  stunning cityscape from the iconic Marina Bay Sands and take in panoramic views of the glittering skyline. Feel the adrenaline rush as you explore the exhilarating rides at Universal Studios Singapore and dive into the vibrant energy of Sentosa Island. From breathtaking vistas to heart-pounding excitement, this tour offers the perfect blend of awe and adventure. Don’t miss your chance to experience the best of Singapore—book \'Singapore Skyline & Thrills\' today and let the adventure begin!','2025-04-20','img/packages/010_Singapore_Resized_jpg/010_img_1020_6.jpg','Singapore Skyline & Thrills',6,5,2000.00,'2025-04-15',5,'img/packages/010_Singapore_Resized_jpg/010_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/010_Singapore_Resized_jpg/010_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/010_Singapore_Resized_jpg/010_img_1020_3.jpg','img/packages/010_Singapore_Resized_jpg/010_img_1020_7.jpg'),(11,'Rev up your excitement with our \'Race to the Lion City\' tour, where the thrill of Formula 1 meets the vibrant energy of Singapore!','Singapore','Rev up your excitement with our \'Race to the Lion City\' tour, where the thrill of Formula 1 meets the vibrant energy of Singapore! Feel the roar of the engines as you get exclusive access to the high-octane Singapore Grand Prix, set against the dazzling backdrop of the city’s skyline. Enjoy premium viewing spots,exhilarating tours and concerts, and VIP experiences that put you in the heart of the action. This is your chance to experience the world’s only night race in style. Don’t miss out—secure your spot on the \'Race to the Lion City\' now and get ready for an unforgettable ride!','2025-09-23','img/packages/011_Singapore_Resized_jpg/011_img_1020_6.jpg','Race to the Lion City: Singapore F1 Experience',5,4,5000.00,'2025-09-19',4,'img/packages/011_Singapore_Resized_jpg/011_img_1020_7.jpg','img/packages/011_Singapore_Resized_jpg/011_img_1020_11.jpg','img/packages/011_Singapore_Resized_jpg/011_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/011_Singapore_Resized_jpg/011_img_1020_4.jpg'),(12,'Indulge your senses with \'The Taste of Bangkok\' tour, a culinary journey through Thailand’s vibrant capital!','Thailand','Indulge your senses with \'The Taste of Bangkok\' tour, a culinary journey through Thailand’s vibrant capital! Discover hidden street food gems and Michellin exmperiences, where the aromas of foods such as  sizzling pad Thai and spicy green curry fill the air. Explore bustling markets, sample exotic fruits, and taste delectable local dishes prepared by master chefs. Immerse yourself in the rich flavors and traditions that make Bangkok a global food lover\'s paradise . Don\'t miss out on this unforgettable gastronomic adventure—reserve your spot on \'The Taste of Bangkok\' today and treat yourself to a feast you’ll never forget!','2025-08-11','img/packages/012_Thailand_Resized_jpg/012_img_1020_4.jpg','The Taste of Bangkok',5,4,2500.00,'2025-08-07',2,'img/packages/012_Thailand_Resized_jpg/012_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/012_Thailand_Resized_jpg/012_img_1020_2.jpg','img/packages/012_Thailand_Resized_jpg/012_img_1020_5.jpg','img/packages/012_Thailand_Resized_jpg/012_img_1020_3.jpg'),(13,'Dive into the vibrant festivities of Thailand’s Songkran festival with our \'Songkran Sawadeee\' tour!','Thailand','Dive into the vibrant festivities of Thailand’s Songkran festival with our \'Songkran Sawadeee\' tour! Join in the exhilarating water fights that transform the streets into a lively splash zone, celebrate with traditional Thai rituals, and soak up the joyous atmosphere of the Thai New Year. Experience the unique blend of fun, culture, and celebration as you immerse yourself in the heart of Songkran\'s colorful traditions. This is your chance to be part of one of the world\'s most exciting festivals. Don’t wait—secure your spot on \'Songkran Sawadeee\' now and make a splash this New Year!','2025-04-15','img/packages/013_Thailand_Resized_jpg/013_img_1020_4.jpg','Songkran Sawadeee',4,3,1800.00,'2025-04-12',3,'img/packages/013_Thailand_Resized_jpg/013_img_1020_1.jpg','img/packages/013_Thailand_Re